{"id": "1494919240111624273", "channel_id": "1494919240111624273", "author_id": "277927692735873035", "author_name": "choco_minnto", "content": "After witnessing the ethereal core incident and AA situation, i think many players have lost hope and trust in biav and its devs.\n\nAs such I would like to ask for myself and on behalf on any other players who might consider quitting the game in the near future. \n\nIs there is a refund policy for unused silver prime? \n\nI feel like this is a reasonable request as it excludes silver prime that has been spent, and this refund practice has been used in recent gacha game that EOS’ed (black beacon).", "timestamp": "2026-04-18T04:35:21.099000+00:00", "thread_id": "1494919240111624273", "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}]}
